_sText:
So this is my first map i have ever bothered to finish and my first release. 

I have "made" some maps before, but 90% of them were just tests for skyboxes and so on.

People who have played CS 1.6 will know this map immediately. I got a lot of inspiration from the map cs_mansion.
ok to be honest. this is almost like a remake of the map. it looks a lot like it, but it still isn't completely the same.  

Anyways, i hope you will enjoy the map as much as enjoyed it while making it.

- Chickenchief

PS: this map is not final. if you have any tips and so on to make it better, please tell me.
